name: Go To Street
description:
In this game it is possible to drive every car in the traffic, to go pub, parfume shop,
private home where your wife always waits you. You have map, which directs you where to go. There is a park, where you can have a walk.

* Traffic system
* Fantastic Graphic
* Beautiful cars
* Grand streets
* Divercity of people
* Reality of human's physics
* Moto ride
